* * * INSTALL SCALA * * *

This program is written in Scala so you need that installed. You
can do that on Linux (Debian/Ubuntu) or OS X by doing the following

  Ubuntu (Hardy)      : apt-get install scala
  http://packages.ubuntu.com/hardy/scala
  
  OS X (with Macports): sudo port install scala 
  http://scala.darwinports.com/

For Windows see http://www.scala-lang.org/node/310.

* * * Run it * * * 

  mvn test-compile
  env JAVA_OPTS="-Xloggc:/var/tmp/out.gc -Xms1024m -Xmx1024m" scala -classpath \
  target/test-classes:target/classes com.runbam.scalademo.PerformanceHarness 5000000

